        "114": {
            "Icon": "skillicon/icon_skill_tangtang_01",
            "Element": "Cryst",
            "Name": "IMA WAVERIDAAH!",
            "Desc": "Tangtang jumps out from the water and fires a point-blank shot that deals <@ba.cryst>Cryo DMG</> to the enemy and creates a <@ba.key>Waterspout</>.\nCasting the battle skill also consumes all nearby <@ba.key>Whirlpools</> to create additional <@ba.key>Waterspouts</> and <#ba.return>return</> some SP based on the number of Waterspouts created.\n<@ba.key>Waterspout</>: Applies 1 stack of <#ba.crystinflict>Cryo Infliction</> on enemies within range and deals <@ba.cryst>Cryo DMG</> over time. If the battle skill creates multiple <@ba.key>Waterspouts</>, they also apply <#ba.spellvul>Arts Susceptibility</> to enemies (but not another stack of <#ba.crystinflict>Cryo Infliction</>).\n<@ba.info>DMG dealt by the Waterspout is treated as Battle Skill DMG.</>",
